#. Tag: title
#: viewer.docbook:11 viewer.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Viewer"
msgstr "Pregledovalnik"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The reason for you to put all your images into &kphotoalbum;, and spending "
"hours after hours describing them, is of course that you at some point want "
"to look at them. For that purpose &kphotoalbum; has an viewer capable of "
"showing your images and videos. You open the viewer from the thumbnail view "
"as described in <xref linkend=\"chp-thumbnail-view\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Razlog, da vse svoje slike spravite v &kphotoalbum; in preživite ure za "
"urami, ko jih opisujete, je seveda ta, da si jih na neki točki želite "
"ogledati. V ta namen ima &kphotoalbum; pregledovalnik, ki lahko prikaže vaše "
"slike in videoposnetke. Pregledovalnik odprete v pogledu sličic, kot je "
"opisano v <xref linkend=\"chp-thumbnail-view\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "Common Viewer Commands"
msgstr "Pogosti ukazi pregledovalnika"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The viewer supports both images and videos. The following commands are "
"supported for both images and videos:"
msgstr ""
"Pregledovalnik podpira tako slike kot videoposnetke. Naslednji ukazi so "
"podprti tako za slike kot za videoposnetke:"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid "Press <keycap>Esc</keycap> to close the viewer window."
msgstr "Pritisnite <keycap>Esc</keycap>, da zaprete okno pregledovalnika."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press either <keycap>Page Down</keycap> or the <keycap>Space</keycap> bar to "
"move to the next image or video, and press <keycap>Page Up</keycap> to move "
"to the previous image or video."
msgstr ""
"Za premik na naslednjo sliko ali videoposnetek pritisnite tipko <keycap>Page "
"Down</keycap> ali <keycap>Preslednica</keycap>, za premik na prejšnjo sliko "
"ali videoposnetek pa tipko <keycap>Page Up</keycap>."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>1</keycap></keycombo> to open the <link "
"linkend=\"chp-typingIn\">annotation dialog</link> for the current image or "
"video."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>1</keycap></keycombo>, da odprete <link "
"linkend=\"chp-typingIn\">pogovorno okno za opombe</link> za trenutno sliko "
"ali videoposnetek."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>4</keycap></keycombo> to set the image or "
"video as the first in its stack (if it is already part of a stack)."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>4</keycap></keycombo>, da sliko ali "
"videoposnetek nastavite kot prvo v skladu (če je že del sklada)."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>d</keycap></keycombo> to edit the image "
"description."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>d</keycap></keycombo> za urejanje opisa "
"slike."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press either <keycap>&Enter;</keycap> or <keycap>F11</keycap> to toggle full "
"screen mode while viewing an image or video."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite <keycap>&Enter;</keycap> ali <keycap>F11</keycap> za preklop v "
"celozaslonski način med ogledom slike ali videoposnetka."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press <keycap>Delete</keycap> to remove the current image or video from the "
"viewer list (as if you hadn't selected it for viewing) and advance to the "
"next item in the viewer list. If the last image or video in the viewer list "
"is removed, the viewer window is closed."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite <keycap>Delete</keycap>, da odstranite trenutno sliko ali "
"videoposnetek s seznama pregledovalnika (kot da ga ne bi izbrali za ogled) "
"in se premaknete na naslednji element na seznamu pregledovalnika. Če je "
"zadnja slika ali videoposnetek na seznamu pregledovalnika odstranjen, se "
"okno pregledovalnika zapre."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Delete</keycap></keycombo> to add the current "
"image or video to the viewer's deletion list. When the viewer window is "
"closed, &kphotoalbum; will open the <emphasis>Removing Items</emphasis> "
"dialog if the deletion list is not empty."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Izbriši</keycap></keycombo>, da trenutno "
"sliko ali videoposnetek dodate na seznam za brisanje v pregledovalniku. Ko "
"je okno pregledovalnika zaprto, bo &kphotoalbum; odprl pogovorno okno "
"<emphasis>Odstranjevanje elementov</emphasis>, če seznam za brisanje ni "
"prazen."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "Viewing Images"
msgstr "Ogled slik"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See <xref linkend=\"sect-viewer-common-commands\"/> for viewer commands "
"supported for both images and videos."
msgstr ""
"Glejte <xref linkend=\"sect-viewer-common-commands\"/> za ukaze za "
"pregledovanje, ki so podprti za slike in videoposnetke."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The viewer can be seen in <xref linkend=\"fig-viewer\"/>. The viewer does of "
"course show you the image, but in addition to that it also shows you the "
"information you specified for each image, including who is in the image, "
"where and when it was taken, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Pregledovalnik si lahko ogledate v <xref linkend=\"fig-viewer\"/>. "
"Pregledovalnik vam seveda prikaže sliko, vendar vam poleg tega prikaže tudi "
"informacije, ki ste jih določili za vsako sliko, vključno s tem, kdo je na "
"slikah, kje in kdaj je bila posneta, &etc;"

#. Tag: title
#: viewer.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Info Box"
msgstr "Informacijsko polje"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The viewer provides an info box which can be overlaid on top of the image. "
"The info box is positioned at the bottom center in <xref linkend=\"fig-viewer"
"\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Pregledovalnik ponuja informacijsko polje, ki ga je mogoče prekriti čez "
"sliko. Informacijsko polje je postavljeno na spodnji srednji rob v <xref "
"linkend=\"fig-viewer\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the info box is located on top of part of the image you actually want to "
"see, you can click the &LMB; on the info box and drag it elsewhere on the "
"image. Press <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>i</keycap></keycombo> to toggle the "
"info box on or off."
msgstr ""
"Če se informacijsko polje nahaja na vrhu dela slike, ki ga dejansko želite "
"videti, lahko kliknete z levo tipko miške na informacijsko polje in ga "
"povlečete drugam na sliko. Pritisnite <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>i</keycap></"
"keycombo>, da vklopite ali izklopite informacijsko polje."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to configure what should be shown in the info box, and of "
"course whether it should be shown at all. All these options are available by "
"clicking the &RMB; on the viewer. The context menu can be seen in <xref "
"linkend=\"fig-viewer-contextmenu\"/> below."
msgstr ""
"Možno je nastaviti, kaj naj se prikaže v informacijskem polju in ali naj se "
"sploh prikaže. Vse te možnosti so na voljo s klikom na &RMB; v "
"pregledovalniku. Kontekstni meni si lahko ogledate spodaj v <xref linkend="
"\"fig-viewer-contextmenu\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid "The viewer's context menu"
msgstr "Kontekstni meni pregledovalnika"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some of the words in the info box are underlined. If you click the &LMB; on "
"one of these words, the browser (see <xref linkend=\"chp-browsing\"/>) will "
"go into the scope of that item. For example, in the demo if you click on "
"<literal>Anne Helene</literal> in the info box, the browser will show you "
"all images of Anne Helene, just as it would have done if you selected "
"<literal>People</literal> from the root of the browser, and next selected "
"<literal>Anne Helene</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Nekatere besede v informacijskem polju so podčrtane. Če kliknete z levo "
"tipko miške na eno od teh besed, bo brskalnik (glejte <xref linkend=\"chp-"
"browsing\"/>) prešel v obseg tega elementa. Če na primer v predstavitvi v "
"informacijskem polju kliknete <literal>Anne Helene</literal>, vam bo "
"brskalnik prikazal vse slike Anne Helene, tako kot če bi v korenu brskalnika "
"izbrali <literal>Ljudje</literal> in nato izbrali <literal>Anne Helene</"
"literal>."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the top right-hand corner of the info box you can see a small "
"<emphasis>Jump to Context</emphasis> button with the &kphotoalbum; logo. "
"Clicking the &LMB; on this button will navigate to the <xref linkend=\"chp-"
"thumbnail-view\"/>. The thumbnail view will display all images, and the "
"image you just had in the viewer will be selected. The idea behind this is "
"the following: you browse to a given person, and look at the images of that "
"person. One of the images is from say your high school time, and now you "
"want to see images from that period of time. Using the <guilabel>Jump to "
"Context</guilabel> button, you are brought to the thumbnail view showing all "
"images, with the current one being in focus and likely all your high school "
"pictures around it."
msgstr ""
"V zgornjem desnem kotu informacijskega polja lahko vidite majhen gumb "
"<emphasis>Skoči na kontekst</emphasis> z logotipom &kphotoalbum;. S klikom "
"na &LMB; se boste pomaknili na <xref linkend=\"chp-thumbnail-view\"/>. V "
"pogledu sličic bodo prikazane vse slike in izbrana bo slika, ki ste jo "
"pravkar imeli v pregledovalniku. Ideja je naslednja: poiščete določeno osebo "
"in si ogledate slike te osebe. Ena od slik je recimo iz časa vaše srednje "
"šole in zdaj si želite ogledati slike iz tega obdobja. Z gumbom "
"<guilabel>Skoči na kontekst</guilabel> se odpre pogled sličic, ki prikazuje "
"vse slike, pri čemer je trenutna v fokusu, okoli nje pa so verjetno vse vaše "
"slike iz srednje šole."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the current image has geolocation coordinates, you will see a map button "
"below the <guilabel>Jump to Context</guilabel> button in the info box. "
"Clicking the &LMB; on this button will open a new window with a map showing "
"where the photograph was taken."
msgstr ""
"Če ima trenutna slika geolokacijske koordinate, boste pod gumbom "
"<guilabel>Skoči na kontekst</guilabel> v informacijskem polju videli gumb "
"zemljevida. S klikom na ta gumb z levo tipko miške se odpre novo okno z "
"zemljevidom, ki prikazuje, kje je bila fotografija posneta."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The map button is only displayed if &kphotoalbum; was compiled with &marble; "
"support."
msgstr ""
"Gumb za zemljevid se prikaže le, če je bil &kphotoalbum; preveden s podporo "
"za &marble;."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid "Viewing More Images"
msgstr "Ogled več slik"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In case you have loaded several images into the viewer, in addition to "
"moving forward and backward using <keycap>Page Up</keycap> and <keycap>Page "
"Down</keycap> keys, respectively, you can go to the first and last images "
"using <keycap>Home</keycap> and <keycap>End</keycap>. These functions are of "
"course also available from the context menu."
msgstr ""
"Če ste v pregledovalnik naložili več slik, se lahko poleg premikanja naprej "
"in nazaj s tipkama <keycap>PageUp</keycap> in <keycap>PageDown</keycap> "
"premaknete na prvo in zadnjo sliko s tipkama <keycap>Home</keycap> in "
"<keycap>End</keycap>. Te funkcije so seveda na voljo tudi v kontekstnem "
"meniju."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can display multiple images as a slide show. In slide "
"show mode, &kphotoalbum; loads a new image into the viewer every few "
"seconds. Press <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>r</keycap></keycombo> to toggle the "
"slide show on or off. Press <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>+</keycap></keycombo> to "
"make the slide show go faster or <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>-</keycap></"
"keycombo> to make it go slower."
msgstr ""
"Lahko pa prikažete več slik kot predstavitev. V načinu predstavitve "
"&kphotoalbum; naloži novo sliko v pregledovalnik vsakih nekaj sekund. "
"Pritisnite <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>r</keycap></keycombo>, da vklopite ali "
"izklopite predstavitev. Pritisnite <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>+</keycap></"
"keycombo>, da pospešite predstavitev, ali <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>-</"
"keycap></keycombo>, da jo upočasnite."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid "Zooming In and Out"
msgstr "Povečevanje in pomanjševanje"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the viewer, you may zoom in and out of your image by dragging out a "
"rectangle with the &LMB;. Pressing the <keycap>minus</keycap> key will zoom "
"out again. Pressing the <keycap>plus</keycap> key will zoom in at the center "
"of the image. <xref linkend=\"fig-marking-zoom-rectangle\"/> below shows how "
"a zoom rectangle is marked, and <xref linkend=\"fig-zoomed-view\"/> shows "
"the result of the zoom."
msgstr ""
"Z uporabo pregledovalnika lahko sliko povečate ali pomanjšate tako, da z "
"&LMB; povlečete pravokotnik. S pritiskom tipke <keycap>minus</keycap> sliko "
"ponovno pomanjšate. S pritiskom tipke <keycap>plus</keycap> sliko povečate "
"na sredini. <xref linkend=\"fig-marking-zoom-rectangle\"/> spodaj prikazuje, "
"kako je označen pravokotnik za povečavo, <xref linkend=\"fig-zoomed-view\"/> "
"pa rezultat povečave."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <keycap>period</keycap> key to reset the zoom level so the image "
"is shown at its normal size. Pressing the <keycap>=</keycap> key will set "
"the zoom level so each pixel on the screen correspond to a pixel in the "
"image."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite tipko <keycap>pika</keycap>, da ponastavite stopnjo povečave, "
"tako da je slika prikazana v običajni velikosti. S pritiskom tipke "
"<keycap>=</keycap> nastavite stopnjo povečave tako, da vsaka slikovna pika "
"na zaslonu ustreza slikovni piki na sliki."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer.docbook:194 viewer.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "Zooming in the viewer"
msgstr "Povečanje v pregledovalniku"

#. Tag: title
#: viewer.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rotating Images"
msgstr "Vrtenje slik"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <keycap>7</keycap> key to rotate the image 90 degrees to the left. "
"The <keycap>9</keycap> key rotates the image 90 degrees to the right. The "
"<keycap>8</keycap> key rotates the image 180 degrees (&ie; flips it upside "
"down)."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite tipko <keycap>7</keycap>, da sliko zasukate za 90 stopinj v levo. "
"Tipka <keycap>9</keycap> sliko zasuka za 90 stopinj v desno. Tipka "
"<keycap>8</keycap> sliko zasuka za 180 stopinj (tj. obrne jo na glavo)."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid "Any change to an image's rotation in the viewer is persistent."
msgstr "Vsaka sprememba vrtenja slike v pregledovalniku je trajna."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "Viewing Videos"
msgstr "Ogled videoposnetkov"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See <xref linkend=\"sect-viewer-common-commands\"/> for viewer commands "
"supported for both videos and images."
msgstr ""
"Oglejte si <xref linkend=\"sect-viewer-common-commands\"/> za ukaze za ogled "
"tako videoposnetkov kot slik."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a video is loaded into the viewer, the video starts playing "
"automatically. Press the <keycap>p</keycap> key to pause the video, and "
"press it again to resume video playback."
msgstr ""
"Ko se videoposnetek naloži v pregledovalnik, se predvajanje začne samodejno. "
"Pritisnite tipko <keycap>p</keycap>, da začasno ustavite predvajanje, in jo "
"pritisnite znova, da nadaljujete s predvajanjem."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press <keycap>Home</keycap> to restart the current video from the beginning, "
"and <keycap>End</keycap> stops the current video and rewinds it to the "
"beginning."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite <keycap>Home</keycap>, da ponovno zaženete trenutni videoposnetek "
"od začetka, <keycap>End</keycap> pa ustavi trenutni videoposnetek in ga "
"previje nazaj na začetek."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid "Some viewer features are not available when viewing a video:"
msgstr ""
"Nekatere zmožnosti ogledovalnika niso na voljo med ogledom videoposnetka:"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid "The info box can not be displayed on a video."
msgstr "Informacijskega polja ni mogoče prikazati na videoposnetku."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Zooming operations other than toggling full-screen mode are not supported "
"for videos."
msgstr ""
"Povečave, razen preklopa celozaslonskega načina, za videoposnetke niso "
"podprte."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rotation operations are not supported for videos."
msgstr "Vrtenje videoposnetkov ni podprto."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid "Slide show mode is not supported for videos."
msgstr "Način predstavitev ni podprt za videoposnetke."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Both tokens (see <xref linkend=\"assigning-tokens-from-the-viewer\"/>) and "
"tags (see <xref linkend=\"annotating-from-the-viewer\"/>) can be toggled "
"when a video is displayed in the viewer, but there is no immediate user "
"feedback that anything has changed. You can set the viewer annotation mode "
"to <emphasis>Locked</emphasis> to avoid accidentally toggling a token or tag."
msgstr ""
"Žetone (glejte <xref linkend=\"assigning-tokens-from-the-viewer\"/>) in "
"oznake (glejte <xref linkend=\"annotating-from-the-viewer\"/>) je mogoče "
"preklopiti, ko je videoposnetek prikazan v pregledovalniku, vendar uporabnik "
"ne prejme takojšnje povratne informacije o tem, ali se je kaj spremenilo. "
"Način opomb v pregledovalniku lahko nastavite na <emphasis>Zaklenjeno</"
"emphasis>, da preprečite nenamerno preklapljanje žetona ali oznake."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As noted above, the <keycap>p</keycap> key is used to toggle pause so it is "
"not possible to use this key to toggle a token or tag while viewing a video."
msgstr ""
"Kot je navedeno zgoraj, se tipka <keycap>p</keycap> uporablja za preklop med "
"premorom, zato te tipke ni mogoče uporabiti za preklop žetona ali oznake med "
"ogledom videoposnetka."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid "Video Seeking"
msgstr "Iskanje videoposnetkov"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The viewer supports seeking within a video. The key bindings are listed in "
"the <xref linkend=\"table-video-seek-controls\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Ogledovalnik podpira iskanje znotraj videoposnetka. Vezave tipk so navedene "
"v <xref linkend=\"table-video-seek-controls\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer.docbook:287
#, no-c-format
msgid "Video Seek Controls"
msgstr "Kontrolniki za iskanje videoposnetkov"

#. Tag: entry
#: viewer.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid "Seek Duration"
msgstr "Trajanje iskanja"

#. Tag: entry
#: viewer.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "Seek Backward"
msgstr "Išči nazaj"

#. Tag: entry
#: viewer.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid "Seek Forward"
msgstr "Išči naprej"

#. Tag: entry
#: viewer.docbook:298
#, no-c-format
msgid "100 msec"
msgstr "100 msec"

#. Tag: keycombo
#: viewer.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Shift;<keycap>&Up;</keycap>"
msgstr "&Shift;<keycap>&Up;</keycap>"

#. Tag: keycombo
#: viewer.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Shift;<keycap>&Down;</keycap>"
msgstr "&Shift;<keycap>&Down;</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: viewer.docbook:303
#, no-c-format
msgid "1 sec"
msgstr "1 sec"

#. Tag: keycap
#: viewer.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Up;"
msgstr "&Up;"

#. Tag: keycap
#: viewer.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Down;"
msgstr "&Down;"

#. Tag: entry
#: viewer.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid "10 sec"
msgstr "10 sec"

#. Tag: keycap
#: viewer.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Left;"
msgstr "&Left;"

